    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This unit maintains factory-spec compression across all six cylinders with a recently overhauled VANOS system and shimmed valves for optimal timing. The chassis is structurally immaculate, having undergone proactive subframe reinforcement with TMS plates. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual to a refreshed M-Variable limited-slip differential. Suspension geometry remains true with fresh bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the telepathic handling these chassis are known for. No fluid weeping, no pixel loss, and a pristine underside. This is a collector-grade example for the discerning driver who values mechanical transparency.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
