      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most rigorous inspection. This car has been climate-control garaged since day one and treated with a multi-stage professional ceramic coating, resulting in a deep, mirror-like paint finish completely free of swirl marks, chips, or imperfections. The interior is a time capsule; the premium leather seats show no bolster wear, the carpets are protected by original factory mats, and the cabin retains its original new-car fragrance. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a documented service history with every maintenance interval performed ahead of schedule. From the pristine engine bay to the untouched alloy wheels, every detail reflects a life of pampered ownership. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade example that drives as tightly and smoothly as the day it left the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
