      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and only doing hand washes. It\u2019s in pristine shape, inside and out, and it still even has that fresh new-car smell! I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
